Ramiz did not show up. On the 24th Ramiz called and again wanted me to call CGW with a bogus transmission claim.

I have now removed the low pressure fuel pump and installed his original fuel pump at his request. He does not want to pay for a fuel pump. We also put $10 gasoline due to the right side of the fuel tank being empty. This is because the fuel pump is faulty and will not transfer fuel to the right side where the pick up is.

We did not find any codes in the transmission or shifter. The reduced power/chassis malfunction warning on his dashboard is caused by the fuel pump. Right now the vehicle will start until the right side of the fuel tank runs out of fuel.
